## 4. DOMAIN ARCHITECTURE & DATA SCHEMA

The core engine is the **AvantLessonPlayer**. All content is driven by a canonical JSON structure.

### Canonical Question JSON Schema (Semantic Format - RECOMMENDED)

**CRITICAL:** Use the **semantic JSON format** which decouples content from presentation. This reduces JSON size by 40-60% and improves scalability.

```typescript
interface ModuloEstudo {
  meta: {
    banca: string;      // e.g., "FGV"
    ano: string;        // e.g., "2024"
    orgao: string;      // e.g., "TRIBUNAL"
    prova: string;      // e.g., "Analista Judiciário"
    topico: string;     // e.g., "Português"
    subtopico: string;  // e.g., "Sintaxe"
  };
  question_data: {
    instruction: string; // Supports HTML (e.g., <strong>)
    text_fragment?: string; // HTML support (sanitized)
    options: Array<{
      id: string; // "A", "B", etc.
      text: string;
      is_correct: boolean;
    }>;
  };
  reverse_study_slides: Array<ReverseStudySlide>;
}

type ReverseStudySlide = 
  | { 
      type: "concept_map";
      subject?: string; // Auto-generates theme
      items: Array<{
        label: string;
        detail?: string;
        icon?: string; // Lucide icon name (validated)
      }>;
      footer_rule?: string;
    }
  | { 
      type: "danger_zone";
      content: string;
      items?: Array<{ label: string; detail?: string }>;
      footer_rule?: string;
    }
  | { 
      type: "golden_rule";
      content: string; // Giant typography
    }
  | { 
      type: "logic_flow";
      steps: string[]; // Numbered logic
    }
  | { 
      type: "syllable_scanner";
      word?: string;
      tonicIndex?: number;
      rule?: string;
    }
  | { 
      type: "versus_arena";
      concept_a?: string;
      concept_b?: string;
    };
```

### NeuroSlides Logic
- **ConceptMap:** Use grid layouts for morphological molecules. Theme auto-generated from `subject`.
- **DangerZone:** Render with Red/Rose themes to signal alert.
- **GoldenRule:** High emphasis, large font size.
- **LogicFlow:** Numbered steps with visual connectors.
- **Theme Generation:** Automatic based on `subject` field (no manual `design_system` needed).

### Legacy Format Support
The system supports backward compatibility with the old format (`structure`, `design_system`, `layout_variant`), but **always prefer the semantic format** for new content.

